--------------------------------------------------------------
0x2000 0000 - 0x2001 0000   4 * 16 kB AHB SRAM      (RamAHB)
--------------------------------------------------------------
0x1008 0000 - 0x1008 A000   32 kB + 8 kB local SRAM (RamLoc40)
--------------------------------------------------------------
0x1000 0000 - 0x1000 8000   32 kB local SRAM        (RamLoc32)
--------------------------------------------------------------
